rows.label: tlk42300013_03_msg0001
rows.name:
It seems the final battle
is upon you, is it not?

rows.label: tlk42300013_03_msg0002
rows.name:
You, who have unraveled the
secret of Captain Nopopon,
will surely be victorious.

rows.label: tlk42300013_03_msg0004
rows.name: I entrust the future of Alst to you...

rows.label: tlk42300013_03_msg0005
rows.name:
I did it, mo! I spoke ancient
Nopon speech perfectly, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300013_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Moh?! I let some modern Nopon
speech slip out... mo.
